## 3. Gap Analysis

### 3.1 Critical Gaps (P0)

| ID | Gap | Impact | Business Need |
|----|-----|--------|---------------|
| GAP-001 | **No comments table** | Users cannot comment on posts | PRD U-031: "As a user, I want to comment on posts" |
| GAP-002 | **No admin permissions system** | Cannot implement granular admin roles | Task requirement: "Roles & permissions" |
| GAP-003 | **No content tags/hashtags** | Limited content discovery | PRD: "Explore/Discover" features |

### 3.2 Medium Gaps (P1)

| ID | Gap | Impact | Business Need |
|----|-----|--------|---------------|
| GAP-004 | **No tips table** | Tips are only in transactions | No dedicated tip tracking/goals |
| GAP-005 | **No subscription history** | Only current subscription tracked | Cannot analyze subscription patterns |
| GAP-006 | **No user activity tracking** | Limited engagement analytics | PRD: "Audience insights" |
| GAP-007 | **No content bundles table** | Cannot implement bundle purchases | PRD P1 feature |

### 3.3 Future Gaps (P2)

| ID | Gap | Impact | Business Need |
|----|-----|--------|---------------|
| GAP-008 | No referral system | Cannot track creator/user referrals | BRD: Referral program |
| GAP-009 | No promotional codes | Cannot offer discounts | Future marketing |
| GAP-010 | No creator verification badges | Limited trust signals | PRD: Creator badges |

