## 8. Risks

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Missing comments feature blocks launch | High | High | Add comments table in schema |
| Admin permissions insufficient | Medium | Medium | Design permissions system |
| Transaction table scaling | Medium | High | Plan partitioning strategy |
| Message table scaling | High | High | Plan partitioning strategy |
| JSONB fields become unmanageable | Low | Medium | Document expected structure |

